name: ENDiagnosisReportType
desc: The type of a report that describes the origin of a diagnosis.

items.name: case confirmedClinicalDiagnosis
items.desc: The report comes from a confirmed clinical diagnosis.

items.name: case confirmedTest
items.desc: The report comes from a confirmed test.

items.name: case recursive
items.desc: The report comes from a person determined positive based on exposure to another person confirmed positive.

items.name: case revoked
items.desc: The report is a negative test.

items.name: case selfReported
items.desc: The report comes from the user, without health authority involvement.

items.name: case unknown
items.desc: The report is an unknown type or is not available.
